%C3%B4ng-ki%E1%BA%BFn-qu%C3%A1/poem-Tz8vWHWQkWWRTYQ4Xaqoyw">Thù chư công kiến quá - 酬諸公見過</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2m-Th%C3%BAc-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Thu%E1%BA%BF-quan-dao/poem-iIlbYlGUZwIlaYEVrRT92A">Thuế quan dao - 稅官謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A2m-Th%C3%BAc-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-wX2bDmkie6Brb76otqww3g">Khâm Thúc Dương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-L%C3%A3ng/T%C3%B4n-ti%E1%BB%81n-mi%E1%BB%85n-huynh-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/poem--hkU94lAyWZTM_fbPQJxUw">Tôn tiền miễn huynh trưởng - 樽前勉兄長</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-L%C3%A3ng/author-QcVcrL73Uo9raEQzmrL0vA">Phan Lãng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Chi/V%E1%BB%8Dng-gia-th%C6%B0/poem-Q0TAkuuOaVash8qnVD-2lA">Vọng gia thư - 望家書</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Chi/author-PDwspC721eAeaL3MOQf-eA">Lý Chi</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
